{"title_page": "American Dad! (season 15)", "text_new": "{{short description|Season of television series}}\n{{Infobox television season\n| season_number = 14\n| bgcolour      = #2FCE1F\n| image         =\n| image_alt     = \n| caption       = \n| country       = United States\n| num_episodes  = 22\n| network       = [[TBS (U.S. TV channel)|TBS]]\n| first_aired   = {{Start date|2017|12|25}}\n| last_aired    = {{End date|2019|4|8}}\n| episode_list  = List of American Dad! episodes\n}}\n''[[American Dad!]]''{{'s}} fourteenth season began with a [[Christmas]] special, which aired on December 25, 2017<ref>{{cite press release |title=TBS Schedules \"American Dad!\" Christmas Special for Monday, December 25 |url=http://www.thefutoncritic.com/news/2017/12/07/tbs-schedules-american-dad-christmas-special-for-monday-december-25-15212/20171207tbs01/ |publisher=Turner Broadcasting System, Inc.  |date=2018-12-07 |access-date=2018-03-05}}</ref> on [[TBS (U.S. TV channel)|TBS]]. The season would officially premiere on February 12, 2018, and conclude on April 8, 2019.<ref>{{cite press release |date=2018-01-11 |title=TBS Announces New Monday Night Animation Block with Season Premiere of \"American Dad!\" and Series Premiere of \"Final Space\" |url=http://www.thefutoncritic.com/news/2018/01/11/tbs-announces-new-monday-night-animation-block-with-season-premiere-of-american-dad-and-series-premiere-of-final-space-708511/20180111tbs02/ |publisher=Turner Broadcasting System, Inc.  |access-date=2018-03-05}}</ref> The series went on hiatus after the season's thirteenth episode aired May 7, 2018. The remaining 9 episodes of the season would begin airing on February 11, 2019.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.denofgeek.com/us/tv/american-dad/276801/american-dad-to-air-31-episodes-in-2019|title=American Dad To Air 31 Episodes in 2019|first1=Daniel|last1=Kurland|date=October 7, 2018|publisher=Den of Geek|accessdate=October 6, 2018}}</ref>\n\n==Episodes==\n{{see also|List of American Dad! episodes}}\